2026-05-15T01:06:48.1250601Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1251437Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1252576Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1253434Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1254316Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
