2026-05-15T01:06:48.1259346Z 22    <!--
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1259957Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1260655Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1261295Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1262087Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1262868Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1263645Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1264417Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1265209Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1265976Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1266969Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-05-15T01:06:48.1267532Z 33    -->
