2026-05-15T01:06:48.5255529Z 26            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-15T01:06:48.5255872Z 27          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-15T01:06:48.5256231Z 28            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-15T01:06:48.5256934Z 29        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
